    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level, you gain the ability to reap life energy from creatures you kill with your spells. Once per turn when you reduce one or more creatures to 0 hit points with a spell of 1st level or higher, you regain hit points equal to twice the spell's level, or three times its level if the spell belongs to the School of Necromancy. You don't gain this benefit for killing constructs or undead.</p>",
